{"type": "article", "id": 1351, "title": "这个设计了不起之今日最佳", "description": "我们尝试推荐一些最近发现的聪明设计。好设计并不只是一种装饰，它还是人们对于生活细节的各种思考，并且综合了包括技术、商业在内的多种力量。我们希望持续关注这些变化，它是美好生活的动力之一。", "date": "2014-07-04T09:00:00Z", "super_tag": null, "tags": [{"id": 30, "name": "Paul Smith"}, {"id": 1491, "name": "单车"}, {"id": 1492, "name": "钱包"}, {"id": 1409, "name": "厨房"}, {"id": 1493, "name": "安迪·沃霍基金"}, {"id": 179, "name": "星球大战"}], "category": 17, "author": 1218, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 5, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607160240TKCg7cSf2Ej0hya8.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t1.  MERCIAN FIXED-GEAR BIKE by <a href=\"http://www.paulsmith.co.uk/us-en/shop/\" target=\"_blank\">Paul Smith</a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\">设计师 Paul Smith 先生在投身时尚事业之前一直梦想成为一名自行车运动员，所以他设计的单车无疑时髦又专业，加之与英国定制品牌 Mercian 合作，纯手工打磨的金属框架和手工制作的座椅都会让骑行变的舒适又拉风。<a href=\"http://www.mrporter.com/mens/Paul_Smith_531/mercian-fixed-gear-bike/459420?cm_mmc=LinkshareUK-_-QFGLnEolOWg-_-Custom-_-LinkBuilder&amp;siteID=QFGLnEolOWg-rQqmVIh5_kwmk0fF4VHVIw\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里购买</a>。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607160230maB5STpCo1JuENn3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607160231QRjaS8A7lHxGrL4v.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.04375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606071602311LWF9fwYN7bKxzAh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.04375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607160232SbskMecnohzIG6Wp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.04375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607160232JtE7IaNDSpnWVo0O.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.04375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p3\">\r\n\t<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">2.  Nothing Fancy by <a href=\"http://cargocollective.com/chieh\" target=\"_blank\">Chieh Ting Huang</a></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t没有任何针线缝合的皮质钱包，手工课作品一般，灵感来自经典的把纸钞卷成一卷用橡皮筋捆起来的收纳方法。除了钱包，设计理念还用到了零钱袋、iPhone套、卡包和护照夹等等物品上，成为收纳日常零碎的解决方法。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607160233BuapjYATiJCgzsSt.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607160233IfHGd7jrOiENzYnD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607160234HGmyZp2OSaAKVwXl.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607160234XSOof5v0NthYB9Ly.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607160235EPbjy3Szv60GLmnY.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607160235Vl12bdgs49uDTAjE.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p3\">\r\n\t<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">3.  Kitchen by<a href=\"http://store.mjolk.ca/index.php?ishome=1\" target=\"_blank\"> John Baker and Juli Daoust</a></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\">一对多伦多的设计师设计的挪威风格又带点日范儿的厨房，自然平实，充满生活气息，而且很大，让人看上去就很想在那里烹（用）饪（餐）。一些小细节是可以买到的，比如 Jonas Bohlin 设计的铜质枝形吊灯可以<a href=\"http://www.remodelista.com/products/lamp-kvist-6\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里购买</a>；Sori Yanagi 设计的烧水壶<a href=\"http://www.remodelista.com/products/sori-yanagi-kettle\" target=\"_blank\">点这里</a>；Oji Masanori 出品的锅铲篓<a href=\"http://www.remodelista.com/products/oji-masanori-brass-tool-holder-large\" target=\"_blank\">点这里</a>；Oji Masanori 锅垫<a href=\"http://www.remodelista.com/products/bagel-trivet\" target=\"_blank\">点这儿</a> ⋯⋯总之品质生活很贵。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607160236jdmkhuM8sz31EPiD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607160236Kwsibfo1tuX9SZVA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.603125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607160237sdo2NOXnZKUPlbSy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607160237rhwnQEPT64JkpGjD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.609375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607160238I7o5uhLlN8imMZQG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">4.  \"Marilyn\" Surfboard Collection by  <a href=\"http://www.warholfoundation.org/\" target=\"_blank\">Andy Warhol Foundation</a> x <a href=\"http://www.bessellsurf.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Tim Bessel Surfboards</a></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t安迪·沃霍基金和冲浪品牌 Tim Bessel Surfboards 联名推出了名为\"Marilyn\"的冲浪板系列。冲浪板图案来自安迪·沃霍的代表作之一玛丽莲·梦露的波普肖像画，五款不同颜色每款限量 12 只，并且需要 6-8 周的生产时间。<a href=\"http://www.gagosian.com/shop/search/?search_i=marilyn+surf\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里预订</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607160238H9aJ7f8tXQimq0vN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.4015625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t5.  Star Wars Design Icons by <a href=\"http://randomthoughtpattern.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Filipe Carvalho</a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t葡萄牙设计师 Filipe Carvalho 身为星战迷，为自己喜欢的标志性人物设计了极简主意的图标，背景色十分缤纷，Luke、Yoda、Dark Vador等等人物都列为其中，来看看萌版的《星球大战》吧。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607160239n4QSuGrwKIcCAJ2l.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607160239S53s4zfKo6ZqatUE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0703125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\n\n\n"}